title: Wanted
subTitle: The police kill Shibu, an innocent man, after mistaking him to be his lookalike Raja, an assassin. To escape from the police, Raja starts living with Shibu's parents as their son.

title: Crisscross
subTitle: The lives of five women, each with a different life story, get intertwined after a series of disastrous events leads to an introspection.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Tarakasura sends an assassin to kill Mainadevi and plans to frame Lord Shiva. The assassin puts poison in Mainadevi's food.

title: Half Serious
subTitle: An aspiring director who desires to pen down a script focusing on gender imparity, absurdly ends up ignoring his own wife and forgets to observe parity at home.

title: Mishor Rohosyo
subTitle: Al Mamun, an Egyptian business tycoon, asks his friend Kakababu to help him decode some hieroglyphic symbols that will help trace the will of his teacher, Mufti Mohammad.

title: Badsha: The Don
subTitle: A man who aspires to become a gangster arrives in London to achieve his dreams. However, complications arise when he meets a woman and falls in love with her.

title: Josh
subTitle: Indra, a care-free college student, tries to save his best friend's sister, Anuradha, from a dangerous family dispute, but his efforts lead to unexpected and worsening complications.

title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

title: Tulkalam
subTitle: Honest, hard-working villagers fight against the forces of industrialisation threatening to take their land away.

title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: Beadap
subTitle: Rejected by his parents, Pradeep grows up to be a bandit. Over time, he gets into the bad books of the police force and encounters Inspector Neelima, who is none other than his childhood lover.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainadevi holds Lord Shiva responsible for the danger that happened. The devas become shocked when Lord Shiva asks Lord Vishnu to marry Parvati.

title: Bawal
subTitle: An unemployed youngster plans to elope with his lady love after their parents object to their union. However, disaster strikes after he unwittingly kidnaps a gangster's sister during the heist.

title: Debota
subTitle: After getting subjected to injustice since childhood, Rana decides to rob the rich and distribute the wealth amongst the poor. However, things get difficult when he gets accused of killing his lover.

title: Bidroho
subTitle: Uttam's ailing mother dies after not getting proper treatment when the landlord refuses to help them. Later, he decides to exact revenge against the injustice done to him.

title: I Love You
subTitle: A rich boy loves a poor village girl, but when his family insults her, he chooses to leave his wealthy life and move to her simple village to prove his love.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Bondhoo
subTitle: A devoted father stands up to obstacles and fights against all odds to win legal custody of his young son.

title: Romeo vs Juliet
subTitle: Romeo, a rowdy from a small town, meets the woman of his dreams on Facebook. So, he sets out to London, in order to see her in person and win her over.

title: Romeo vs Juliet
subTitle: Romeo, a rowdy from a small town, meets the woman of his dreams on Facebook. So, he sets out to London, in order to see her in person and win her over.

title: Love in Rajasthan
subTitle: Yuvraaj and Protha are from rival colleges and dislike each other. However, when they happen to stay at the same hotel during a field trip, they start developing feelings for each other.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainadevi approaches Narayan and requests him to marry Parvati, and he accepts her proposal. Narayan impersonates Lord Shiva to meet Parvati.

title: Mayer Dibbi
subTitle: Digambar, a businessman, attempts to destroy his rival, Mahendra Pratap Chowdhary. However, things take a turn when Mahendra's son hinders his plans.

title: Saptami
subTitle: Soumya, a young man, falls in love with and marries Saptami, a beautiful woman. He leaves her with a friend to complete his higher studies but returns only to find shocking truths.

title: Bazee-The Challenge
subTitle: A simple man from the village arrives in Kolkata to meet his childhood friend. However, his life turns upside down when he falls in love with a wealthy woman.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: After his wife's demise, a man tries to start over with her estranged family. When he falls in love with his wife's twin, he fears that his efforts to mend broken relations will go to waste.

title: Dada Thakur
subTitle: Gita plans to reunite with her long-estranged father, not knowing that he is waiting for her younger sister, Mita, to return. The two siblings then struggle to win back his trust.

title: Baro Bou
subTitle: Tapan and his wife generously provide for their joint family. However, when the younger brother marries his employer's daughter, he becomes arrogant, which creates a rift within the family.

title: Phande Poriya Boga Kande Re
subTitle: A light-hearted wedding turns tense when buried family rivalries threaten to explode, testing the resolve of a newly arrived son-in-law.
